723170f-a.title: Manhattan: St. Nicholas Terrace - 127th Street
723170f-a.text:
St. Nicholas Terrace, south from about W. 133rd, to 127th
Streets, showing on the right (west side) the grounds of the
Convent of the Sacred Heart. Opposite same is the fenced slope
that is St. Nicholas Park.
July 1928.
Georcce L. Balgue
CEEDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
